name: Snake
tagline: A classic game of snake in Java, along with an AI to play the game.
body:
# snake

## Contributors

@DJMCoder

## What to do with the zip

This is for a APCSA project, so we used BlueJ ([download here](http://www.bluej.org/)). Open the folder in BlueJ, and run main() on the SnakeGame. 

## Using this for code

If you are using this project to learn code or practice code, please keep the following code at the top of the project:

```
/**
 * @author Jin Kim
 * @author David Melisso
 */
```
